{"data":[{"id":560653360,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"2cac466b677ae354356a5306b729ef36","url_token":"synn","name":"宋小狮","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/25c0cdc0c9642e99ae253a3ce544a2a9_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/25c0cdc0c9642e99ae253a3ce544a2a9_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/2cac466b677ae354356a5306b729ef36","user_type":"people","headline":"我不接受你的建议。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560653360","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545877069,"updated_time":1545944995,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e每年参加高考的人数是千万人左右，考入清北的人数大约是两三百人，也就是说比例大约是几万分之一，虽然很困难，但并不是完全没有可能。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可你想证明的哥猜已经提出将近三百年了，三百年里有多少人想要证明而不得？你想过这个比例吗？你觉得证明哥猜比考清北更容易吗？你把三百年里诞生又死去的无数有聪明才智的人放在哪里呢？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561409122,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"98d5ba60b1ca6318340a11557ab0ae1e","url_token":"luyueti1","name":"luyueti1","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4413846ba3a4001768ad62e1766016b0_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4413846ba3a4001768ad62e1766016b0_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/98d5ba60b1ca6318340a11557ab0ae1e","user_type":"people","headline":"何以舟之，惟玉及瑶","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"