f43376b78f2e22a073ec47efbbe7c5e2_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/05e529d2815ba12bfaaac1bd9eae9a2a","user_type":"people","headline":"不知名白日梦想家","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561172327","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545923413,"updated_time":1545923413,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e会被保送，但前提的可能性几乎没有。不过我着实期待你能写出点什打打某些高赞回答的脸，尽管难度很大，但是某些人着实让人不爽啊，何必一定用这么刻薄的语言来劝诫呢。我是学生物的，对高数了解的也不是很深入，但是我觉得题主敢于尝试很好，若是实在不行一定一定要记得回头，好好复习吧，到了好的大学有更多研究机会!\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562369847,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562369847","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546079782,"updated_time":1546094504,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e如果你的方法简单到可以怀疑“是否可以保送”，那就一定不行。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e好好体会一下“伪证”的力量 QwQ\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e哦对了，你一定没有过联赛二试 4 题全部“证明”却只拿到 1 题分数的经历。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561124530,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal"