true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不提数论，你能不能做一道曲面积分让我看看？贴吧多少年前玩剩下的东西，没想到在逼乎还能割到韭菜，真香。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559674015,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a66d5029f21a0b15c7dfbec3b21af1e7","url_token":"tian-jia-wei-80","name":"四号海钟","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8f9fad966bc48b89467b12571946f94a_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8f9fad966bc48b89467b12571946f94a_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a66d5029f21a0b15c7dfbec3b21af1e7","user_type":"people","headline":"搞笑型选手。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559674015","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545750296,"updated_time":1545750296,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"够呛。\u003cbr\u003e我同学初中时就证明出来了，当时我还跟他学来着，结果学了好久哥猜没学会，光学会吹牛逼了。","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561140190,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0f21a177f318b5efb11cb41f263fa061","url_token":"xie-dian-feng","name":"廖尔","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/06bf6627c8bb545728216c3646432494_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/06bf6627c8bb545728216c3646432494_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0f21a177f318b5efb11cb41f263fa061","user_type":"people","headline":"一个普通的中国人","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561140190","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-637ac7db5ca780a51a5b5f4aed5724a2_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545920531,"updated_time":1545920531,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e那是肯定的，我个人认为。因为这是数学届的王冠 ，有些数学家穷尽一生的心血也没能把它证明过证伪，比如陈景润先生，他虽然有所成就，但还是未能把它攻破，就连当年哥德巴赫写信给欧拉请教这个问题，欧拉先生也表示了沉默，好像不久后就去世了，我没记错的话！我觉得如果能解决这一问题，一是能获得数学届的诺贝尔奖——菲尔兹奖，据说或了这个奖，这个人去任何一所高校任教，工资不得低于不知具体几十万的，如果现实一点，他可以去当个老师，边继续学术研究，边养家糊口，了却余生……不管怎样，我觉得高中生要证明哥德巴赫猜想确实是件不容易的事，起码要有下图中的裁缝那样认真、执着才行！！！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f3780b29e933004bf75238684648e2a5_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1125\" data-rawheight=\"1644\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-075bae74291a1891bf6124d65351acf4_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1125\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f3780b29e933004bf75238684648e2a5_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1125'%20height='1644'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1125\" data-rawheight=\"1644\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-075bae74291a1891bf6124d65351acf4_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1125\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f3780b29e933004bf75238684648e2a5_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f3780b29e933004bf75238684648e2a5_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561476436,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c26a5be5e96c8baad325d387057cadc9","url_token":"qing-zhi-34-60-40","name":"青稚","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0d36df666ad312eddeaad5dc593614ab_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0d36df666ad312eddeaad5dc593614ab_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c26a5be5e96c8baad325d387057cadc9","user_type":"people","headline":"梦里一碗青稞酒接过","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561476436","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545970810,"updated_time":1545970810,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我想问问，证明哥猜之前，你知道（1+1）、（1+2）、1+1、1+2的区别吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果不能\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e麻烦把高等数学和初等数论做满分学几个专业词汇再考虑考虑报考新闻与传播学院\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这等人才学数学真是白瞎\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你应该研究热搜的算法，那才是你的天地\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePS：知乎用户不比微博，有真材实料的人多了去了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePPS：我看到题主在一条回答里说“我不敢说我的证明是没有问题的”这句话让我觉得你真的是一个很好的人，思维也很好，但是，我不想鼓励你是因为我看了你的回答，河北大学数学系的相关你要百度？连给招生办校办打电话的意识都没有？开一个数学专栏你什么都不写？问国际上发表数学论文的地方？你的论文不用百度有道你能写几个单词？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我现在觉得你连陈景润先生都论文有几页都不知道\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e或许你有那个能力，但是，你的格局让你别说在清北，随便一个211你都待不下去\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559427074,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"801856350ce3aceb33365628da6e6e8e","url_token":"zhi-hu-qiong-guang-dan","name":"我的路我的世界","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-9aa416475d5f42a5db084e48db1b7307_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-9aa416475d5f42a5db084e48db1b7307_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/801856350ce3aceb33365628da6e6e8e","user_type":"people","headline":"没有什么比没有梦想更可怜的","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559427074","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545725953,"updated_time":1545875747,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我回答这个问题时还只有几个回答，没想到分分钟就炸到这个程度了。二更，这真是一个恐怖的时代。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e=========================================================\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e讲个实际的吧，高中读完，单纯证明哥德巴赫猜想这个名头足以享誉数学界，而你也会因为这个名头进入史册，一个小小的清华北大数学系，怕是都没资格收你。单纯这一项成就，撇开你是高中生还是初中生这些，毕竟都不重要，你就可以冠名数学家三字了。数学教授算个毛，不是每个教授都能叫数学家，但是每个数学家都有资格做教授\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559955361,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"cf676a4c6732e76381397b45684b6a65","url_token":"owtotwo","name":"owtotwo","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3ec83bfef05331bb375aa75beed37597_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3ec83bfef05331bb375aa75beed37597_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/cf676a4c6732e76381397b45684b6a65","user_type":"people","headline":"程序员","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559955361","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545796443,"updated_time":1545796443,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e其实我觉得 “一个高中生证出” 比 “一个高中学历的证出” 是相对来说更吸引人一点\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562152023,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":